OL,4,Cbills at restaurants without paying
OL,6,FA couple have been jailed after
OL,7,Fadmitting a string of dine and dash
OL,8,Foffences which saw them rack up large
OL,9,Fbills at restaurants and leave without
OL,10,Fpaying.
OL,12,FBernard McDonagh, 41, and Ann
OL,13,FMcDonagh, 39, both of Sandfields, Port
OL,14,FTalbot, who used more than 40 aliases
OL,15,Fand 18 dates of birth between them,
OL,16,Fdishonestly obtained food and drink at
OL,17,Ffour restaurants and one takeaway in
OL,18,Fsouth Wales, with the unpaid bills
OL,19,Ftotalling #1,168.70.
