OL,6,FThe couple, who pleaded guilty to five
OL,7,Fjoint charges of fraud, were arrested
OL,8,Fafter images of their scam were posted
OL,9,Fon social media.
OL,11,FAnn McDonagh was jailed for 12 months
OL,12,Fand Bernard McDonagh was jailed for
OL,13,Feight months.
OL,15,FThey ordered three-course meals for
OL,16,Fthemselves and their family including
OL,17,FT-bone steaks and desserts, with some
OL,18,Fbeing sent back uneaten.
