OL,6,F"You would go to restaurants with your
OL,7,Fown family. You would have food and
OL,8,Fdrink served to you to the value of
OL,9,Fhundreds of pounds and then you would
OL,10,Fcynically and brazenly leave without
OL,11,Fpaying.
OL,13,F"You would order the most expensive
OL,14,Fitems on the menu such as steaks in
OL,15,Fthe full knowledge that you had no
OL,16,Fintention whatsoever of paying for
OL,17,Fthem."
