OL,6,FHe said: "There are an awful lot of
OL,7,Fhonest people out there that enjoy
OL,8,Fusing our hospitality premises, but it
OL,9,Fdoes happen. UK Hospitality estimates
OL,10,Fthat every year this type of behaviour
OL,11,Fcosts businesses as much as #10million
